      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum linear-elastic titanium alloy with frictional contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces; model form justified by literature and prior FDA validation studies.",
      "rationale": "Linear-elastic constitutive model for Ti-6Al-4V is appropriate below yield; post-yield behavior captured by bilinear isotropic hardening. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at all interfaces consistent with published tribology data for dry titanium-on-titanium. Model form corroborated by FDA prior validation database for spinal implant FEA."
