      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength measured from 22 Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupons machined from the same bar stock as the test constructs (mean E=114.2 GPa, CV=1.8%). Geometric dimensions from coordinate measuring machine with 5 µm resolution. Specimen-specific FEA models built for each of the 11 constructs, eliminating geometric variability as a confound."
